<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.261357>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Eucopia australis Dana, 1852: preserved empty female from the Bellingshausen Sea in dorsal (A) and lateral (B) view (modified after San Vicente 2010 a). Gnathophausia zoea Willemoës-Suhm, 1873 from Cap Breton (Bay of Biscay): freshly adult male in dorsal (C) and lateral (D) view (original illustration). Lophogaster spinosus Ortmann, 1906 from the Gulf of Cádiz: freshly adult male in dorsal (E) and lateral (F) view (modified after Abelló et al. 2011)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/261357/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

